          ENDIF
.
          DISPLAY   *P35:14,MRMODESC
.
GRES9000  MOVE      ZERO,EXIT
          GOTO      GRES9999
.
GRES9100  MOVE      ONE,EXIT
.
GRES9999  RETURN
